com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.scriptItem.action.response.extractor

Class CookieExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.scriptItem.action.response.extractor.AbstractExtractor
      • com.xceptance.xlt.nocoding.scriptItem.action.response.extractor.CookieExtractor

  • public class CookieExtractor
extends AbstractExtractor
    Extracts the specified cookie from the headers located in Context.getWebResponse(). The cookie is extracted via name provided by AbstractExtractor.getExtractionExpression(). The value of the cookie is then accessible with AbstractExtractor.getResult().
    Author:
    ckeiner
